  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary purpose of this study is to investigate the effectiveness reflected by the&#xD;
      retention rate of perampanel as the only add-on treatment in adult participants with primary&#xD;
      generalized tonic-clonic (PGTC) or secondarily generalized tonic-clonic (SGTC) seizures based&#xD;
      on focal or idiopathic generalized epilepsy in a non-interventional (observational) setting.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
